{"tid":2359324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國隊長、變形俠醫、莎朗史東斥特朗普煽動衝突","createTime":"2021-01-08T21:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T15:46:38.000Z","uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4a151d842e7ceb2890f93eba46acf66be0284fc5","tid":2359324,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T21:04:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/daily/ent/907076/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fent%2F907076%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=b2176a94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fent%2F907076%2F&h=c5ff9231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/daily/ent/907076/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國會昨爆發造成人命傷亡的流血衝突，事緣美國總統特朗普的支持者衝擊國會山莊，拒絕承認國會確認民主黨拜登和賀錦麗當選美國總統及副總統。在美國大選期間曾批評社交網絡平台CEO的歌手Selena Gomez昨再批評YouTube、facebook、Instagram及twitter等高層，炮轟他們未有刪除發放仇恨言論的帳戶，她又點名批評社交平台的高層令美國人失望，並希望他們盡快修補。<br />\n<br />\n　　「美國隊長」基斯伊雲斯 、「變形俠醫」麥克路化奴、「波叔」沙查巴朗高漢、莎朗史東等都表達憤怒及羞恥，並斥特朗普煽動衝突，要求刪除特朗普的社交帳戶。而「美國隊長」基斯亦留言指︰「如果他們（特朗普支持者）不是白人，今天會演變成怎樣的大屠殺？」"},{"pid":"5749de1dbd6d751f10e72288ff706ef5553c35ad","tid":2359324,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T21:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d391abced1257b403f9c32e7acb2847d8d4d4a","tid":2359324,"uid":233905,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T21:06:39.000Z","msg":"Trump: go home<br />\n左膠：trump煽動衝突<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdfdf1453ed097f51c8967d0d7cc11d8e31daad","tid":2359324,"uid":135040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,